HEADWORD: Spadroon
<hw>Spa*droon"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F. & Sp.
<ets>espadon</ets>, It. <ets>spadone</ets>. See <er>Espadon</er>,
